// ŌöĆŌöĆ raw_checkins ņ╗¼ļ¤╝ ĻĄ¼ņĪ░ ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆ
// [0] timestamp  [1] weekTitle  [2] items_json
// [3] userId     [4] weekKey    [5] dateKey  [6] score

function saveCheckin(items, userId, weekKey, dateKey, score, requestId) {
  const cleanItems = Array.isArray(items) ? items.filter(Boolean) : [];
  if (!cleanItems.length) throw new Error('No items selected');

  const today = dateKey || Utilities.formatDate(new Date(), 'Asia/Seoul', 'yyyy-MM-dd');
  const cleanRequestId = cleanRequestId_(requestId);
  const requestCacheKey = cleanRequestId
    ? cacheKey_('submit_' + hashStr(String(userId || '') + '\x00' + weekKey + '\x00' + today + '\x00' + cleanRequestId))
    : '';
  if (requestCacheKey) {
    const cached = cacheGetJson_(requestCacheKey);
    if (cached) return cached;
  }

  const lock = LockService.getScriptLock();
  try { lock.waitLock(10000); } catch(e) { return { ok: false, error: 'ņ×Āņŗ£ Ēøä ļŗżņŗ£ ņŗ£ļÅäĒĢ┤ņŻ╝ņäĖņÜö.' }; }

  try {
  if (requestCacheKey) {
    const cachedAfterWait = cacheGetJson_(requestCacheKey);
    if (cachedAfterWait) return cachedAfterWait;
  }
  const config   = getConfig();
  const effectiveWeekKey = String(weekKey || ('w' + config.currentWeek)).trim();

  // ņä£ļ▓äņé¼ņØ┤ļō£ ņżæļ│Ą ņĀ£ņČ£ ļ░®ņ¦Ć: Events payloadņØś ĒģŹņŖżĒŖĖ + ņØĖļŹ▒ņŖż ļæś ļŗż ņ▓┤Ēü¼
  const submittedToday   = new Set();
  const submittedIndices = new Set();
  const userEvents = Events_readByUser(userId);
  const submittedEvents = getMissionSubmittedEventsForConfig_(userEvents, config, effectiveWeekKey);
  let prevWeekScore = 0;
  if (submittedEvents.length) {
    for (const event of submittedEvents) {
      prevWeekScore += getMissionEventScore_(event);
      if (getMissionEventDateKey_(event) === today) {
        getMissionEventItems_(event).forEach(function(item) {
          submittedToday.add(item);
          const idx = config.items.indexOf(item);
          if (idx >= 0) submittedIndices.add(idx);
        });
        getMissionEventIndices_(event).forEach(function(idx) {
          if (typeof idx === 'number') submittedIndices.add(idx);
        });
      }
    }
  }

  const newItems = cleanItems.filter(item => {
    if (submittedToday.has(item)) return false;
    const idx = config.items.indexOf(item);
    return !(idx >= 0 && submittedIndices.has(idx));
  });

  if (!newItems.length) {
    const duplicateResult = {
      ok: true,
      savedItems: [],
      savedIndices: [],
      newScore: 0,
      weekScore: prevWeekScore,
      ticketEarned: false,
      duplicate: true
    };
    if (requestCacheKey) cachePutJson_(requestCacheKey, duplicateResult, 600);
    return duplicateResult;
  }

  // ņĀÉņłś ņä£ļ▓äņŚÉņä£ ņ×¼Ļ│äņé░
  const newScore = newItems.reduce((s, item) => s + (config.scores[item] || 1), 0);

  // ņØĖļŹ▒ņŖż ņĀĆņ×ź: ĒģŹņŖżĒŖĖ ļ│ĆĻ▓Į ņŗ£ņŚÉļÅä ņĀ£ņČ£ ņØ┤ļĀź ņ£Āņ¦Ć
  const newIndices = newItems.map(item => config.items.indexOf(item));

  // IņŚ┤: ĒĢ┤ļŗ╣ ņŻ╝ņ░© ļłäņĀü ņĀÉņłś (ĻĖ░ņĪ┤ rows ņ×¼ņé¼ņÜ®)
  const weekCumScore = prevWeekScore + newScore;

  // JņŚ┤: ņØ┤ ņĀ£ņČ£ļĪ£ ņ▓śņØī threshold ļŗ¼ņä▒ĒĢśļ®┤ 1, ņĢäļŗłļ®┤ 0
  const ticketEarned = (prevWeekScore < config.drawThreshold && weekCumScore >= config.drawThreshold) ? 1 : 0;

  const now = new Date();
  // mission.submitted (+ ticketEarned ņŗ£ ticket.granted)ļź╝ setValues 1ĒÜīļĪ£ ļ¼ČņØī
  const eventBatch = [{
    type: EVENT_TYPES.MISSION_SUBMITTED,
    userId: userId,
    options: {
      timestamp: now,
      weekKey: effectiveWeekKey,
      payload: {
        weekTitle: config.weekTitle,
        dateKey: today,
        score: newScore,
        weekCumScore: weekCumScore,
        items: newItems,
        indices: newIndices,
      },
      source: EVENT_SOURCES.WEB,
    },
  }];
  if (ticketEarned === 1) {
    eventBatch.push({
      type: EVENT_TYPES.TICKET_GRANTED,
      userId: userId,
      options: {
        timestamp: now,
        timestampOffsetMs: 1,
        amount: 1,
        weekKey: effectiveWeekKey,
        payload: { reason: 'week_complete' },
        source: EVENT_SOURCES.WEB,
      },
    });
  }
  Events_appendBatch_(eventBatch);
  if (ticketEarned === 1) {
    rebuildCollectionRow_(userId);
  }
  clearUserDerivedCaches_(userId);
  const result = {
    ok: true,
    savedItems: newItems,
    savedIndices: newIndices,
    newScore,
    weekScore: weekCumScore,
    ticketEarned: ticketEarned === 1,
    duplicate: false
  };
  if (requestCacheKey) cachePutJson_(requestCacheKey, result, 600);
  return result;
  } finally {
    lock.releaseLock();
  }
}

